data.description: Welcome to your Newest Home Sweet Home with ***PAID OFF SOLAR*** Home Features New Windows, Tankless Water Heater, Ceiling Fans in Every Bedroom, Completely Gated Front and Backyard. As you Enter through the Security Screen Door, the Spacious Updated Kitchen Warmly Welcomes you to Create your First Meal for Family and Friends. The Large Livingroom is then your Next Relaxing place to hangout and look outside the French Doors to your Generously sized Backyard, with a Covered Patio and Covered Gazebo for even More Hangout space. Also included is a Shed for extra storage for garden tools or the She-shed. The Bedrooms are all generously sized with extra Storage Cabinets in the Hallway. The Hallway Bathroom is freshly painted with a shower/tub. Main Bedroom features extra storage cabinets and its own bathroom with a walk-in shower. This Home won't disappoint.
